data.description: This property features two dwellings. The Main House offers 1,342 sq ft. On the first-floor, a spacious living area, dining room and full bath. On the second floor you have 3 bedrooms and a full bath. The basement is finished and could be used as a studio or office space with the possibility to convert into an in-law apartment. The Mobile home is new. Added in 2023, it features up to date living space with convenience and functionality. 765 square feet, 2 bedrooms, 1 and 1/2 baths. The addition of the mobile home to the property provides living options that can serve various purposes. From housing family members to potentially being used as a guest house, rental property, or even a private space for work. The lower outbuilding was constructed in 2012, it offers functional space that can cater to various industries with sanitary requirements. It features floor drains, a hand wash sink and a refrigeration cooler unit. Unique opportunity for commercial rental income with visibility to Rt 1. There is a 2 car garage detached on the property. ***
